	@{u}Environment variables@{uu}

	The following environment variables are known by @{i}CyberGraphX4 @{ui}:

	@{"     " Link "NODE_ENVVAR_ALERTEMU"} ALERTEMU
	@{"     " Link "NODE_ENVVAR_CPUP2C"} CPUP2C
